What if a 🐀, who was so sniveling that it became a toady, was taunted by a 🐜 who was so decisive that it became a decision maker?

The 🐀's detractors were now forming a queue.
#Toady=#Decision_maker

🐀😖👈😄🐜 (or: 🐀 was taunted by 🐜)
So at first, the decisive 🐜 taunted the sniveling 🐀 with cruel jibes.

🐀👅🆙🐜 (or: 🐀 licked up to 🐜)
So the 🐀 licked up to the 🐜.
🐜🖕➡🐀🙂☹ (or: 🐀 was disrespected by 🐜)
But the 🐜 spat in the 🐀's eye.

🐀💵➡🐜 (or: 🐀 paid off 🐜)
So the 🐀 paid the 🐜 to do its bidding.

🐀🆚👤❓🐀👈🐜 (or: 🐀 was favored by 🐜)
Well, the 🐜 openly favored the 🐀.

🐀🤔💬🆚🗨🤔🐜 (or: 🐀 disagreed with 🐜)
Yet the 🐀 expressed strong disagreement with the 🐜.

🐀😖🔚󱕴🗨🐜 (or: 🐀 was fired by 🐜)
"Get out! You're fired" said the 🐜.

🐀➡🐜💀 (or: 🐀 murdered 🐜)
Well, the 🐀 murdered the 🐜 in its bed.

🐀➡🐜💀🔚🚔🔗 (or: 🐀 was arrested for killing 🐜)
So in the end the sniveling 🐀 was arrested for brutally attacking the decisive 🐜.

The 🐜 died soon after and the 🐀 was charged with murder.
The End
